  "notes": {
    "designObservations": "Salesforce CRM page uses a dual-navbar pattern (utility bar + product subnav). Sections alternate between white and very light green (#F4FAF7/#EDF7F2) backgrounds. Cards use a distinctive colored top accent bar to differentiate product categories. Hero section uses split-color heading (dark + brand green). AI chatbot FAB is persistent bottom-right. Product illustrations use flat vector characters on circular colored backgrounds. Decorative SVG landscapes appear between sections.",
    "recommendedFonts": ["Source Sans Pro", "Inter", "DM Sans"],
    "googleFontsURL": "https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Source+Sans+Pro:wght@400;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap",
    "animationLibraries": ["css-only", "framer-motion for scroll reveals"],
    "componentLibrary": "custom (or shadcn/ui as base)",
    "implementationNotes": "1) Implement dual navbar — sticky sub-nav after scroll. 2) Use CSS custom properties from cssVariables section. 3) Card top accent bars use different green/teal shades per product. 4) All interactive states need transition: all 0.2s ease. 5) Form validation shows green checkmark inside input on valid. 6) Chat FAB is fixed position bottom-right. 7) Section backgrounds alternate #FFFFFF and #EDF7F2. 8) Replace Salesforce Sans with Source Sans Pro or Inter from Google Fonts."
  }
